Module com.example.demo

Package com.example.demo.endGameElements

package com.example.demo.endGameElements
package that houses the elements that are used in the end game screen, also is the package that has the class to determine if a new highscore has been set.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    EndGame
    The main class for the end game scene itself and is the core for all operations relating to the end game scene, albeit there only being a few functionalities.
    endGameVisuals
    This class' main functionality is to display the visual elements within the end game screen, those being mainly the score, the relevant texts and a button for the user to quit the game.
    highScore
    The highscore class is utilized through its function of determining if a new highscore is made after each user's gaming session.
